{
  "stem": "25287.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one day with, one day without.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we, in a dark-- almost evening-- somehow, the-- sometimes they let to stop us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, they said, rush, rush, rush.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And was like a fork.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my sister, one of the lager-sisters, falled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And Erzsabet help her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we don't realize, when they send us this way, then she's not behind us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we find that out in the evening, my younger sister and I, we really don't want to live, anymore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You went through more than a year, and then lost her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't remember how many-- I think was two weeks, because May 8, when we arrived to there, there was two nice men with us-- one of them was in-- in the Red Cross-- and a couple of women.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, one day we was with-- with some police, and next day was wasn't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day we slept in a forest, next day in a barn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] May 8, we was walking and walking, in a rainy day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we arrived to Zerbst.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every house was burned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in the window was a white sheet, that mean they already liberated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we walk, and if not these two men-- and a couple-- I don't think so my sister and I, we survive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they-- they did-- once in a while, you know, we was hungry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They put some bread, or something on the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the field.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then they know [INAUDIBLE], and then we should go and get it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And finally, we saw the American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they took us to a-- a school, where many people was there, what we can eat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But that time, I was very sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't hardly walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
